OL,3,CEluned Morgan likens herself to
OL,4,Cstrawberry daiquiri, warning she could
OL,5,Close seat
OL,7,FWales's Labour First Minister likened
OL,8,Fherself to a strawberry daiquiri as
OL,9,Fshe warned constituents she could lose
OL,10,Fher seat in the Senedd election.
OL,12,FBaroness Eluned Morgan, the leader of
OL,13,FWelsh Labour, said in a video posted
OL,14,Fon social media there was a "danger"
OL,15,Fof her losing to a Reform candidate.
OL,26,@vD@]OUvD@dO]
