OL,3,CEluned Morgan likens herself to
OL,4,Cstrawberry daiquiri, warning she could
OL,5,Close seat
OL,7,FLabour has led Wales for more than two
OL,8,Fdecades but Plaid Cymru and Reform are
OL,9,Fneck and neck according to the latest
OL,10,Fpoll by ITV Cymru Wales, with Labour
OL,11,Fin a distant third. The poll forecast
OL,12,FWelsh Labour to win 12 seats, but none
OL,13,Fin Eluned Morgan's Ceredigion Penfro
OL,14,Fconstituency.
OL,16,FIn the video, the Labour First
OL,17,FMinister used canned cocktails to
OL,18,Fexplain the new voting system in
OL,19,FWales, in which constituents will be
OL,20,Frepresented by six members of the
OL,21,FSenedd.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
