OL,3,CEluned Morgan likens herself to
OL,4,Cstrawberry daiquiri, warning she could
OL,5,Close seat
OL,7,FEluned Morgan said: "So, in Ceredigion
OL,8,FPenfro we know that Plaid is pretty
OL,9,Fsecure, they've got at least two
OL,10,Fseats, maybe even a third, so, they're
OL,11,Fgood. Ceredigion ` Plaid is really
OL,12,Fstrong.
OL,14,F"So, the real battle is between
OL,15,FReform, the Tories and Labour.
OL,17,F"So, in the latest poll... I'm in.
OL,18,FBut, it won't necessarily stay that
OL,19,Fway unless you come out and vote
OL,20,FLabour."
OL,26,@oD@UOUvD@AOUyD@AOU|D@HO]
