PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1777205471
OL,3,CEluned Morgan likens herself to
OL,4,Cstrawberry daiquiri, warning she could
OL,5,Close seat
OL,7,F"That's me," the First Minister said,
OL,8,Fholding a canned strawberry daiquiri
OL,9,Fup to the camera.
OL,11,FShe used a mojito to represent Plaid
OL,12,FCymru, a blue raspberry martini for
OL,13,Fthe Conservatives, an espresso martini
OL,14,Ffor Reform, a pina colada for the
OL,15,FGreens, and an Irn-Bru vodka martini
OL,16,Ffor the Welsh Liberal Democrats.
OL,18,F"Because the real danger is that if
OL,19,Fyou don't come out and don't support
OL,20,FLabour, you're going to get another
OL,21,FReform person," Lady Morgan added.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@LO]zD@AOU}D@OO]
