OL,3,CEluned Morgan likens herself to
OL,4,Cstrawberry daiquiri, warning she could
OL,5,Close seat
OL,7,F"God knows who that is, and you're
OL,8,Fgoing to lose somebody who really
OL,9,Fknows how the Senedd works, who's ran
OL,10,FWales and who represents this area."
